citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:15 - 11:45
am on 01/14/2015.
Inspector knocked on resident door, honked GOV horn and called listed phone number with no response.
